{"tid":845249,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《延禧攻略》編劇于正打造《皓鑭傳》，魏瓔珞與乾隆再續前緣","createTime":"2018-10-02T13:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T06:57:18.000Z","uid":206895,"like":11,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"09c9f463114c7fbe04f59bc087528ac7f2234ede","tid":845249,"uid":206895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"《延禧攻略》完美收官，機智伶俐的「魏瓔珞」正式落幕，讓一眾追劇戲迷大感空虛。不過，劇迷們不會寂寞太久，皆因《延禧攻略》原班班底打造的《皓鑭傳》早在 4 月便完成拍攝，上映日期指日可待。在編劇于正的率領下，《延禧攻略》的部分演員將會「再續前緣」，繼續合作。《延禧攻略》的演員們將由清朝倒流回到《皓鑭傳》戰國晚期秦趙爭鋒的時期。（魏瓔珞）吳謹言將會在《皓鑭傳》中再次擔任第一女主角「李皓鑭」（即秦始皇母親），與二位男主角（乾隆皇帝）聶遠「呂不韋」和新加盟的演員茅子俊「嬴異人」開展一段盤根交錯的三角虐戀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/203459_fbc9849b826f43e391d853100f4d3187.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F203459_fbc9849b826f43e391d853100f4d3187.jpg&h=46551904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《皓鑭傳》講述戰國晚期，趙秦二國爭鋒的時段，吳謹言飾演的「李皓鑭」是趙國御史之女，因遭受繼母的陷害而身敗名裂，甚至被賤賣給人口販子。之後遇到聶遠所飾演的「呂不韋」將她買下，並獻給在趙國皇宮當人質的秦國太子「嬴異人」茅子俊。其後，三人各自為了自己的目的結為聯盟，合力離開戰國後，共創戰國最高權力巔峰，並輔助後來的嬴政（秦始皇）為千古一帝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/204037_83080552afa45c2633d0f21dee717763.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F204037_83080552afa45c2633d0f21dee717763.jpg&h=091c0b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相比起《延禧攻略》中的清朝扮相，吳謹言在《皓鑭傳》中的造型更受好評。在劇中，「李皓鑭」吳謹言將繼續反傳統，不做個「傻白甜」女主角，而是與「魏瓔珞」同出一轍，不甘受人欺負，面對黑暗勢力的鬥爭依舊會強硬反擊。《皓鑭傳》中非傳統的女主角性格，一定能讓觀眾看得痛快、過癮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/204223_461af3508cf727ed86dac2ad98a67065.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F204223_461af3508cf727ed86dac2ad98a67065.jpg&h=e8f1b290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而在《皓鑭傳》中「乾隆皇帝」聶遠將會卸下皇帝身分，飾演一個野心勃勃的商人「呂不韋」。計謀多多的「呂不韋」造型更多變，前期充滿俠客氣息，後期因權傾朝野，其造型則更為霸氣。聶遠在《皓鑭傳》中定能展現出與「乾隆皇帝」絕不相同的魅力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/204432_674adfbc56615a847648f25e4f340e04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F204432_674adfbc56615a847648f25e4f340e04.jpg&h=366ce694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/204446_0ed51a825e191e9edc9c53e72e9c1846.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F204446_0ed51a825e191e9edc9c53e72e9c1846.jpeg&h=b8691008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除了「魏瓔珞」吳謹言和「乾隆皇帝」聶遠有份出演，《延禧攻略》中的「高貴妃」譚卓、「明玉」姜梓新、「袁春望」王茂蕾等均有份參與《皓鑭傳》。《延禧攻略》中的讓人恨得咬牙切齒的太監「袁春望」則將變身為「秦孝文王」，與「高貴妃」飾演的「華陽夫人」為夫妻。他們身為「嬴異人」茅子俊的父母，也是「李皓鑭」吳謹言的老爺和奶奶，昔日「魏瓔珞」的仇敵們，變為她的翁媳和婆媳關係。而「魏瓔珞」的好朋友「明玉」也會出現在此劇，化身名為「殷小春」的女子。<br />\n可惜，深受觀眾喜愛的「富察皇后」秦嵐、「富察傅恆」許凱、「嫻妃」佘詩曼等都沒有參與《皓鑭傳》的演出，成為《延禧攻略》戲迷的一大遺憾。"},{"pid":"8d7af27d999d75efad5165b94c7e0812836c3d2c","tid":845249,"uid":53705,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到戰國時代, 都仲要玩後官爭寵"},{"pid":"c743944ebd0b1cdd25d39632b9d3af4b1e497f80","tid":845249,"uid":15730,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:48:19.000Z","msg":"皇帝好型喎<br />\n高貴妃個look幾討好"},{"pid":"3969d5d777bec91eee1def6866f1d8d1a5f70cfc","tid":845249,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:49:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ee31586954ad1f0d93d1efec1a8634646b24ed6","tid":845249,"uid":46678,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:55:38.000Z","msg":"項少龍邊個做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122110a3a08bb330381bbfd3f491da77afd7fd0d","tid":845249,"uid":166062,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T14:04:40.000Z","msg":"高寧馨 明玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a856618c76609808675f81ee51119caedda6cf","tid":845249,"uid":206895,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T14:13:47.000Z","msg":"《皓鑭傳》在服裝造型設計上，對不同國家不同身份的角色做了明顯區分。趙國多以白色的服飾為主，凸顯趙人的浪漫溫婉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/220629_19e4aec426e47415c1ec18ac4349c9f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F220629_19e4aec426e47415c1ec18ac4349c9f2.jpg&h=fc3c5786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/220050_294288c92a41fdc631b75afa95607680.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F220050_294288c92a41fdc631b75afa95607680.jpg&h=4ff155f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇中趙國宮殿運用了石環、浮雕等元素，白色的基調配以圓頂的設計恢弘大氣，不僅將趙王的威權顯得愈發突出，更顯趙國人浪漫溫婉的氣質。而劇情轉入秦國後，劇組則多采用黑色、紅色並配以獸型圖案的服飾，凸顯秦人的霸氣和豪放。該劇為拍攝搭建多達400個場景，里里外外共花費8個月的時間，其中最大的一個場景接近三萬平。<br />\n該劇導演李達超曾執導《建軍大業》《美人為餡》等多部優秀作品的拍攝；編劇爾迪與於正是第二次合作，其編劇的《雲巔之上》因為對娛樂圈行業的刻骨描畫而獲得好評；美術指導鐘移風曾獲得第12屆香港電影金像獎最佳美術指導提名；造型指導宋曉濤因在《鳳囚凰》《延禧攻略》中極具匠心的設計獲得過多方好評。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/220657_4a39008f3918a6b3fed83ab53b079e97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F220657_4a39008f3918a6b3fed83ab53b079e97.jpg&h=99713843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與呂不韋同為男主角之一的嬴異人，秦莊襄王，秦始皇嬴政之父，由茅子俊出演<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/220838_75836c4949fb3d8fd6fe5affa6345fdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F220838_75836c4949fb3d8fd6fe5affa6345fdb.jpg&h=4e245c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公主雅，趙國公主，單戀嬴異人，由海鈴出演<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/221150_c0dad4ceb4146c3f99df3bdb4948dd40.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F221150_c0dad4ceb4146c3f99df3bdb4948dd40.jpeg&h=f8ddac19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n厲夫人，趙國皇后，由寧靜出演"},{"pid":"52a2033d902eafcd2bc202cf0fa44702a13d2fad","tid":845249,"uid":60023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"除左欣賞下服裝設計 其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e739ea1a3867620d9dc1438f12c32aa1e61a13bd","tid":845249,"uid":97909,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/204432_674adfbc56615a847648f25e4f340e04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F204432_674adfbc56615a847648f25e4f340e04.jpg&h=366ce694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n明玉明明靚到痴咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a150dac2a68553215e2e4803e2f38d77edc86293","tid":845249,"uid":126784,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:14:26.000Z","msg":"竟然冇皇后<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7511fd6ddf656f2233d79a1bc72f9734180a7fc","tid":845249,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:20:12.000Z","msg":"4月拍完, 幾時做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8ad511ce679f4a24e4ae7541eb953f56e085cc","tid":845249,"uid":82558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:42:05.000Z","msg":"即係做朱姬喇，邊個做嫪毐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e124dba8e070399426a9e866c025c99b6ecdc01","tid":845249,"uid":49853,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"唔搵林峰做嬴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal